[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "那個人，比以前見過的任何人都要美麗且耀眼……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就像綻放於夏日的花朵一樣──讓我有這種感覺。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0026.wav"], "content": "好熱……好熱呀喵～！快、快點去海邊……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就算妳喊熱，溫度也不會因此降低喔。安靜點快走吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "謝斯大人真好喵……穿得那麼清涼……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "喵一身毛茸茸的，非常不散熱的喵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "唔喵！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "呀啊！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "真是的……誰叫妳不好好走路，才會發生這種事。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0009.wav"], "content": "我家的貓失禮了。有沒有受傷呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……好漂亮。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0048.wav"], "content": "啊，對不起。因為我從來沒看過像大姐姐這麼漂亮的人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "呵呵，我很喜歡坦率的孩子喲。好了，凱特西。還不賠罪。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0047.wav"], "content": "唔嗚……對不起喵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不過，謝斯大人。錯的不只有喵啊。因為這女孩呆站在道路正中間……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0061.wav"], "content": "那是因為……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妳剛才一直仰望著這間屋子的窗戶呢。我記得，這裡是鎮長的宅邸吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "而且鎮長似乎還有一位兒子……他就是妳的心上人嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "妳、妳怎麼知道……！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "看來我猜對了呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "我只是看著而已……我知道我們居住的世界不同。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不下令就不行嗎？我、只是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "昔日的謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "只是、想和李弗一起……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "昔日的謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "身分的差距、嗎……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "從宅邸的圍牆跳到那扇窗戶，貓應該辦得到吧，凱特西。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這個，是沒錯……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0080.wav"], "content": "那麼，帶一隻貓過來。最好是個動作靈巧的孩子。好了，快去。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0015.wav"], "content": "還是老樣子，很會使喚貓呢……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妳會寫字嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0029.wav"], "content": "會、會一點……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0082.wav"], "content": "那就夠了。那麼，我們走吧。首先要準備信紙才行……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "請、請問……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "作為不小心撞到妳的賠禮，我決定幫妳一把。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "我可是很擅長這種事的喲？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "幾天後", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0026.wav"], "content": "呼、呼……！總算找到妳了！那個時候的大姐姐……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "哎呀，妳是前陣子的……貴安。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "妳、妳好……比起那個，妳快看！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0060.wav"], "content": "是之前那封信的回信，對吧。這封信怎麼了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "咦咦！？他竟然回信給我了耶！？而且還寫說希望我再寫信給他！這種事……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "這點程度都在我預料中喔。由貓咪送到窗邊的神秘信箋，以及富有教養的文筆……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "無論任何人都會想知道寄件人是誰。更何況對方還是好奇心旺盛的男孩。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "大姐姐曾經見過他嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "沒見過。但即使素未謀面，也有無數知道的事喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0016.wav"], "content": "好厲害……感覺大姐姐比我更了解他呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "我啊，以前受過他的幫助。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那時店裡有商品不見，結果我被誤會是小偷。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我無父無母，又很窮……當時沒有一個人肯相信我……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但在現場的人群裡面，只有他站在我這邊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "原本只要能站在窗下看著就很滿足，但現在收到了回信，讓我變得想知道更多關於他的事……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0083.wav"], "content": "所以，大姐姐，拜託妳！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "請妳幫助我實現戀情吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "永遠待在我身邊，守護我。只有你得永遠和我站在同一邊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "昔日的謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "明白嗎？這些，並非命令……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "昔日的謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0053.wav"], "content": "等一下喵！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "謝斯大人是來這個鎮上度假的喵。才不接受這種麻煩事……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "安靜，凱特西。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "喵咦！？謝斯大人！？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0014.wav"], "content": "好吧。利用我的智略，一定會讓妳的戀情開花結果。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這、這是吹了什麼風喵？妳竟然理會這麼一個骯髒的小女孩。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "心中的戀慕可不分貴賤喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "……大姐姐，妳是什麼人？應該、是很了不起的人吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……這些，也和妳的戀情無關。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "在這個鎮上，我只是位普通的大姐姐兼妳的戀情顧問。這樣便已足夠了不是嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "唔、嗯……說得也是。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0027.wav"], "content": "很好……那麼，讓我們開始吧。今夏的戀愛講座！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "於是，就這樣開始了。我和大姐姐共度的夏天，和閃閃發光的故事──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 100015081, "title": "綻放夏日之花 (100015081)"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0017.wav"], "content": "好厲害……好厲害喔，大姐姐！全部都照大姐姐說的發展耶！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "今天他在信上寫說想跟我見面！好像在做夢……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "現在可不是興奮到忘我的時候喔。接下來才要開始呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "我知道。等我、見到他之後，就會好好將心意說出來……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "唉，真是不像話呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？不對嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "錯得徹底。如果由自己告白，最後只會被認為是個輕浮的女人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "至少得抱持「讓對方告白」的想法才行呀。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0036.wav"], "content": "可是，是我先喜歡上他的，那種事……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "高嶺之花絕不會輕易讓人攀折。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "正因其堅韌與高潔，才會吸引他人、讓人渴望得到。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "成為高嶺之花吧。如此一來，對方的心自然也會……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "可是，我既無父無母，又很窮。沒辦法像大姐姐那樣……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "好了，照我說的去做就是。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然後，到了約會當天……", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120017_story/VO_CHR_120017_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "妳在信上推薦的書，我看了喔。非常有趣呢！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120017_01.png", "speakerName": "少年", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（關於那本書的事……是照大姐姐的指示寫的。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（雖然之後向大姐姐借來看過，但有太多不會的字，結果連一半都沒看懂……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（當時還向大姐姐撒謊說看得懂，如果早知道會這樣，就不應該逞強，老實告訴她的……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妳最喜歡哪一段呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120017_01.png", "speakerName": "少年", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "我、我最喜歡……一開始的部分吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "咦？一開始是指出發冒險之前？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120017_01.png", "speakerName": "少年", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "唔、嗯……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120017_story/VO_CHR_120017_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "這、這樣啊。我很喜歡跟怪物戰鬥的部分說……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120017_01.png", "speakerName": "少年", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（我不知道有那一段。因為，我根本看不懂。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "妳知道的事，都很有趣呢。在信上也是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120017_01.png", "speakerName": "少年", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（信，只是照大姐姐說的去寫而已。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（其實我根本不有趣，更不是什麼高嶺之花。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（就連今天，我明明那麼期待。現在卻感覺像一直在說謊似的，完全開心不起來。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（他好像也很困惑。這樣下去，他一定不會再跟我見面了。既然如此……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0081.wav"], "content": "那、那個……我有件事，想告訴你──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0003.wav"], "content": "嗚嗚……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不要隨便流淚。只會讓自己變得不體面而己喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "所以，發生什麼事了？雖然我大致猜得到，但還是姑且問一聲吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我、告訴他「我喜歡你」了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然後呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "他跟我說「對不起」……然後我就逃走了……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "唉……這場戀愛本來就不可能以正面進攻得到結果。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為了想辦法讓它開花結果，我才拿出所有方法的說……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0035.wav"], "content": "我知道啊！可是……感覺、簡直不像我自己的戀愛嘛。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0009.wav"], "content": "對不起，大姐姐……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120062_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "……真是傷腦筋喵。明明是那女孩自己拜託說想要建議的。對吧，謝斯大人？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是啊。要是利用我的智略，想讓幼稚的戀情開花結果，再容易不過。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但是，這也代表那並非她想要的正確答案吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為了達到期望的結果不擇手段──我這樣的做法，對純真的孩子而言或許過於激烈也說不定。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "所以呢？夏天的講座要到此為止了喵？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "怎麼可能。我的確不純真，相反地卻相當思慮周密喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "夏天現在才剛開始呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 100015082, "title": "昔日的純情 (100015082)"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "我已經，不再是會讓感情與話語失控的小孩子了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "要說我已失去純真、變得汙穢，或許也不為過吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "即便如此，我仍然對現在的我感到驕傲。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "正因如此，我才無法原諒──", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0008.wav"], "content": "但話說回來……真不像謝斯大人的作風喵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "對一個連指示都無法遵守的小女孩，根本沒必要做到這種地步喵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "不，這是我身為大人的堅持。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "唔唔？什麼意思呢喵？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為了達到期望的結果不擇手段──我可無法忍受被人認為這種大人的做法沒有夢想呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "即使不純真也能逐夢。不如說，有些夢正因身為大人才能實現。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這件事，我必須告訴那孩子才行。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "謝斯大人還是老樣子，很不服輸喵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "那當然。畢竟敗北可不適合我呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "好了，開始下一步吧。夏日舞會即將揭幕了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0060.wav"], "content": "這裡是……？這件禮服是……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0049.wav"], "content": "閉上嘴跟喵走吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "…………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（好像走進童話故事一樣……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "打擾了喵。喵帶那孩子來了喵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊啊，就是這孩子嗎……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "貴族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "請問、這位是……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "是願意領養無父無母的妳，成為妳養父的人喵～", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "養父……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "嗨，初次見面。我聽王女大人提過妳的事。希望妳務必成為我家的孩子……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "貴族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "王女大人是……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊啊，她來了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "貴族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "阿爾貝利亞王家第三王女……謝斯王女大人喵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "貴安。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "王女大人……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（在水晶吊燈下微笑的大姐姐，比在太陽下時更加漂亮了……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "嚇了我一跳……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不滿嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "沒有。只是嚇了一跳……謝謝……您。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0032.wav"], "content": "威爾登侯爵是位心地善良的人。想必不會虧待妳的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這下舞台已準備完畢。盡情展現妳的心意吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "咦？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "真是個遲鈍的孩子呢。這樣一來，阻礙妳戀情的事物就消失了吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "為了這個目的，才讓我成為貴族？為什麼要為我做這麼多……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因為我無法原諒，妳那彷彿擁有純真才是正確的表現。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "所以，我決定要讓妳親眼見識看看。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "看看狡猾的大人才能實現的頂級美夢。覺得如何呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "夢……的確，好像在做夢一樣。感覺自己閃閃發光，彷彿變成了童話故事中的登場人物……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "是啊，新的篇章即將開始。而妳將由少女蛻變為大人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "接下來，妳將正式踏入社交界。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "在輝煌璀璨的水晶吊燈下，充滿大人們蠢動的黑暗思緒。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "若永遠保持純真，則會在剎那間被吞噬殆盡。想必妳也無法永遠是個純真的孩子吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "若妳有即使如此也想得到的東西，有想完成的事情……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "向前邁進，踏入舞池吧。在水晶吊燈下成為比任何人都耀眼的存在，並贏得妳想要的事物吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "就像我一樣……這就是，我給妳最後的建議。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "謝謝妳……我走了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "好的，一路順風。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "歡迎來到，大人的世界。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 100015083, "title": "盛夏舞會 (100015083)"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "夏夜漸深，舞會也將散場……", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120040_story/VO_CHR_120040_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "好了，向王女致謝並道別吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120040_01.png", "speakerName": "貴族", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "謝謝妳，大姐姐……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_120062_story/VO_CHR_120062_STORY_0045.wav"], "content": "不，非常感謝您。謝斯王女大人。再見。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/120109_01.png", "speakerName": "女孩", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "好的。後會有期。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "無父無母的貧困少女，突然變身貴族的女兒……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0039.wav"], "content": "真的會順利喵？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0040.wav"], "content": "這點我倒是不擔心喔。那孩子雖然還不夠成熟，但非常聰明。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不僅靠自己學會了讀書寫字，也懂得看對象改變態度和語氣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "想必再過幾年，就會成為我可愛的小貓咪吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0006.wav"], "content": "喵喵！？難不成謝斯大人，妳從一開始目的就是……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "那當然。我可沒有空閒到幫人處理領養事宜這麼麻煩的事，卻不求一點回報呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "不愧是謝斯大人。雖然是常有的事，卻還是令喵很佩服喵……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "隔天", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊！這麼說來，謝斯大人。難得來度假一趟，卻一直在照顧那個小女孩喵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0084.wav"], "content": "只剩下幾天能停留在這裡。今年夏天，有沒有什麼遺憾喵？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "夏天的遺憾、嗎……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為什麼李弗不能跟我們一起去海邊呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "昔日的謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因為這次是屬於王家的假期。而且，他還有工作要做。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "昔日的雷歐尼特", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……一點也不有趣。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "昔日的謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（結果，我從沒和李弗一起來過海邊呢。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（被問到夏天的遺憾，竟然會想起這麼久以前的事，看來我還是不夠成熟……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0033.wav"], "content": "我沒有任何遺憾喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "況且也沒有什麼特別的預定，剩下的日子就悠閒地度過……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100018_story/VO_CHR_100018_STORY_0010.wav"], "content": "打擾了，謝斯大人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "？？？", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……你、怎麼會在這裡？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "好久不見了，謝斯大人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100018_story/VO_CHR_100018_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "我帶來雷歐尼特大人的信。…………謝斯大人？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0005.wav"], "content": "啊……好的，是信對吧。遠道而來，辛苦你了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（李弗只是為工作而來。況且，我也已經不是小孩子了……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那麼，先告辭……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……！等、等等！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（明明、已經不是小孩子了……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（但是我、為什麼會忍不住叫住他呢！？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_01.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 100015084, "title": "夏日的遺憾 (100015084)"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "李弗前來將信交給謝斯。正當李弗打算回去時，謝斯卻突然叫住了他……", "isSys": true, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "SYS", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100018_story/VO_CHR_100018_STORY_0042.wav"], "content": "……謝斯大人？怎麼了嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0058.wav"], "content": "啊……那個……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……………………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "兩人", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（事到如今不管說什麼藉口，都只會讓自己顯得不體面吧。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（話雖如此，也不能就這樣一直保持沉默……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0041.wav"], "content": "咳咳。沒什麼事。你何不早點回去？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（現在我只能、這麼說了吧……）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我原先是這麼打算的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "但今天還是在這個鎮上留宿一晚吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0059.wav"], "content": "……！？為、為什麼……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我忘記雷歐尼特大人曾指示過，要我「偶爾好好放鬆一下。」", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "若我立刻回去，將會違背雷歐尼特大人的命令。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0023.wav"], "content": "連休假都得下令……真像你呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（我還以為被他察覺了某些事，但李弗的話根本不必擔心吧。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（那如果，這樣呢……？）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0083.wav"], "content": "既然如此，今晚陪我散散步吧。沒問題吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "遵命。那麼，今夜我將前去迎接您。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……………………", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "請小心腳邊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0011.wav"], "content": "嗯……夜晚的海灘好安靜。是屬於大人的時間呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100018_story/VO_CHR_100018_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "的確。能清楚地聽見海浪的聲音。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "對你說些拐彎抹角的話也沒用，我就開門見山地問了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "為什麼，你會決定在這個鎮上留宿一晚呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100018_story/VO_CHR_100018_STORY_0061.wav"], "content": "這……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你原本打算立刻回去的。之所以改變行程，是因為我不小心說出奇怪的話嗎？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "是的……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "真是不成熟啊。就連我自己也不曉得，為什麼會脫口而出那麼幼稚的話。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我已經是大人了。必須注意別做出不謹慎的發言才行……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "正因是那樣的發言，才讓我決定今晚留宿這個鎮上的。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因為我感覺，那句話是出自您的真心。而我已經許久沒聽見您坦率的話語了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "令我忽然想起過去。年幼的您曾哭著說，想與我一同前來海邊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……唔！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0074.wav"], "content": "那、那麼久以前的事我早就不記得了。你也快點忘了吧。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100018_story/VO_CHR_100018_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "不，我記得很清楚。您確實曾有過純真的孩童時代。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "正因如此，有時會令我擔心。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "擔心？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "您已成長為大人。正確地說，是不得不成長為大人。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0030.wav"], "content": "是啊。身為立於人上者是當然的。不成熟之人可無法引導國家。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這點十分令人敬佩。但是，我認為您應該也可以有個暫時放鬆的場所。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "讓您回歸坦率、純真的時候……我認為您應該可以享受這樣的短暫時光。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0073.wav"], "content": "……是嗎。既然如此，我今晚能不能向你撒嬌呢？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "若謝斯大人如此期望。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "我是服侍您，以及阿爾貝利亞的騎士。有任何事請儘管吩咐。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100018_story/VO_CHR_100018_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "我永遠與您站在同一邊。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0025.wav"], "content": "……唉，你這個人實在是……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "你應該多少向我學習一下，如何察覺別人話中所帶的意思比較好喔。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "畢竟，你也已經是個大人了。請你明白？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "算了。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "啊，謝斯大人……！請別擅自到處亂跑……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（策略什麼的對李弗來說沒用。所以，也沒必要使用。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "（也因此，只有和你在一起的時光，才讓我覺得能稍微變回純真的少女。）", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "謝斯大人！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "一直碎碎唸的太煩人囉！現在可是難得的假期呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "何況我身邊還有個可靠的騎士……放鬆一點也沒關係吧？", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "……是。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "那……我們來玩吧！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_drg_200013_story/VO_DRG_200013_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "看來夏日回憶綻放了喵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "這樣一來應該就沒有遺憾了吧喵。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/dragon/200013_01.png", "speakerName": "凱特西", "type": "conversation"}, {"type": "break"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "謝斯大人，請有所節制……！", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100018_03.png", "speakerName": "李弗", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": ["vo_chr_100015_story/VO_CHR_100015_STORY_0004.wav"], "content": "我還沒玩夠喲。夜晚才正要開始呢。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": "story/chara/100015_09.png", "speakerName": "謝斯", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 100015085, "title": "於月下盡情盛開 (100015085)"}]